No Restrictions: There are no offshoring restrictions. All functions including those that involve processing of Member Protected Health Information (e.g.Claims Adjudication, etc.).

No Live Member Touch: This will restrict the following types of services from going offshore: Member Telephonic Service, Live Chat, TeleHealth, etc...

The following functions will be allowed to go offshore: Claims Adjudication, Enrollment & Billing, Correspondence Processing, PaymentIntegrity, GroupReporting, Application Maintenance (Lights-On), Benefit Coding, Case Installation, Provider Credentialing, Contract Pricing & Configuration, Front-End, etc.

No PHI Processing: This will restrict the following types of services from going offshore: Member Telephonic Service, Provider Telephonic Service, Live Chat, TeleHealth, Claims Adjudication, Enrollment & Billing, Correspondence Processing, Payment Integrity, Group Reporting, etc.

The following functions will be allowed to go offshore: Benefit Coding, Case Installation, Provider Credentialing, Contract Pricing & Configuration, Front-End, etc
